Title:          lirc.tcz
Description:    Linux Infrared Remote Control
Version:        0.8.6
Author:         Karsten Scheibler & Christoph Bartelmus
Original-site:  http://www.lirc.org
Copying-policy: GPL
Size:		256k
Extension_by:   robc
Comments:	A config file is needed for a remote/tv. The
		default location of this file is /etc/lirc.conf.	
		There are many remote/tv config files available 
		at the lirc website. Otherwise use irrecord and 
		follow the instructions.
		Inluded modules:
			lirc_atiusb
			lirc_bt829
			lirc_dev
			lirc_ene0100
			lirc_i2c
			lirc_igorplugusb
			lirc_imon
			lirc_it87
			lirc_ite8709
			lirc_mceusb
			lirc_sasem
			lirc_serial
			lirc_sir
			lirc_streamzap
			lirc_ttusbir
			lirc_wpc8769l
		
		----------------------------------------------
		
		Please see the man page for additional 
		information. 
		
		Also see http://www.lirc.org 
		for more information.
		
		----------------------------------------------
		
		This extension is PPI compatible.
		
